Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:28.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Feeling your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:32.14,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}人は生まれながら光と影を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.84,0:22:43.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}光と影を纏い続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:46.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Their only one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:51.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Feeling your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:54.85,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}欲しいもの全て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:59.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}手に入れること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.22,0:23:06.16,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}それが幸せなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:11.07,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}誰かが笑顔なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:17.44,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}どこかできっと泣いてる人がいて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:28.75,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}すれ違うほど　愛おしく思う気持ちがある
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.12,0:23:33.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}ひとときのあいだに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:40.31,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}僕らはみんな矛盾を抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:48.49,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}あしたへの光を見つめながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.73,0:23:52.81,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}歩いてくのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:32.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}人类从出生开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.84,0:22:43.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就一直缠绕着光与影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:54.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}将一切想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:59.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}都收入囊中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.22,0:23:06.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那真的就幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:11.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如果有人在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:17.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那一定在某处也有人在哭泣着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:28.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}每当擦肩而过 就会觉得怜爱不已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.12,0:23:33.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在转瞬而逝的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:40.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我们都会怀抱着矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:48.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}能够一直看着通向明天的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.73,0:23:52.81,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一直走下去吗
